trans-unit.source: Provides a simple listener that directs logging output to file.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en enkel lytter som angir at logging utdata til fil.

trans-unit.source: The FileLogTraceListener class provides automated maintenance capabilities to archive log files as needed, on a daily or per-application basis.
trans-unit.target: Klassen FileLogTraceListener har funksjoner for automatisk Vedlikehold arkivere loggfiler etter behov, daglig eller per-program.

trans-unit.source: This automatic archival functionality helps reduce the maintenance responsibilities of developers and administrators.
trans-unit.target: Denne funksjonaliteten for automatisk arkivering reduserer Vedlikehold ansvaret for utviklere og administratorer.

trans-unit.source: An instance of FileLogTraceListener can be added to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collections to redirect output from logging to a text file.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av FileLogTraceListener kan legges til i <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samlinger å omdirigere utdata fra logging til en tekstfil.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Instances of this class can also be added to `My.Application.Log` or `My.Log` (for Web applications) in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)] applications.
trans-unit.target: Forekomster av denne klassen kan også være lagt til `My.Application.Log` eller `My.Log` (for webprogrammer) i [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)] programmer.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Walkthrough: Changing Where My.Application.Log Writes Information](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)`.` The main features of this class are: 1.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [gjennomgang: endre der My.Application.Log skriver informasjon](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) `.` hoved funksjonene i denne klassen, er: 1.

trans-unit.source: *Archival functionality*.
trans-unit.target: *Arkivering funksjonalitet*.

trans-unit.source: The log files generated by this class are named according to the base name and the date, along with a number to distinguish the log file from successive versions of the log.
trans-unit.target: Loggfilene som genereres av denne klassen er navngitte i henhold til navnet på base og datoen sammen med et tall til å skille mellom loggfilen fra etterfølgende versjoner av loggen.

trans-unit.source: New log files are created on an as-needed basis.
trans-unit.target: Nye loggfiler opprettes på etter behov.

trans-unit.source: The explicit form of the file name is `baseName`[-`dateStamp`][-`version`].log, where: - The `baseName` part is the fundamental log name, specified by the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.BaseFileName%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Eksplisitt formatet filnavnet er `baseName`[-`dateStamp`] [-`version`] log, der: - `baseName` del er grunnleggende loggnavnet, angitt av den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.BaseFileName%2A>egenskapen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.BaseFileName%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The `dateStamp` part has the format "YYYY-MM-DD", and it is shown when <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A> is <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption> or <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption>.
trans-unit.target: - `dateStamp` Del har formatet "Åååå-MM-DD", og det vises når <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A>eller <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption> <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption>.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A>

trans-unit.source: - If more than one log file is needed with the same `baseName` and `dateStamp`, the `version` part, a positive `Integer`, is added to the file name.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis du trenger mer enn én loggfil med samme `baseName` og `dateStamp`, `version` del, et positivt `Integer`, legges til filnavnet.

trans-unit.source: *Multiple class instances*.
trans-unit.target: *Flere klasseforekomster*.

trans-unit.source: If an instance of the FileLogTraceListener class writes to a file that is in use: - The class shares the file if it is being used by another instance of the FileLogTraceListener class in the same process.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en forekomst av klassen FileLogTraceListener skriver til en fil som er i bruk:-klassen deler filen hvis den er i bruk av en annen forekomst av klassen FileLogTraceListener i den samme prosessen.

trans-unit.source: - The class creates a new log file using the next available name if the file is being used by another process.
trans-unit.target: -Klasse oppretter en ny loggfil med navnet på neste tilgjengelige hvis filen er i bruk av en annen prosess.

trans-unit.source: *Thread safety*.
trans-unit.target: *Tråd sikkerhetsnivået*.

trans-unit.source: The FileLogTraceListener class is thread safe.
trans-unit.target: Klassen FileLogTraceListener er trygt tråd.

trans-unit.source: This allows you to safely write messages to the log from multiple threads without using locks.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør at du kan skrive trygt meldinger i loggen fra flere tråder uten å bruke låser.

trans-unit.source: **Log-File Location** - The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Location%2A> property takes a <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileLocation> enumeration to specify one of the typical directories to write the log file to.
trans-unit.target: **Loggen filplasseringen** - <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Location%2A>egenskapen tar en <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileLocation>opplistingen til å angi ett av de vanlige mappene å skrive til loggfilen for å.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileLocation> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Location%2A>

trans-unit.source: - To write the log to another location, set the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.CustomLocation%2A> property to that location.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis du vil skrive loggen til en annen plassering, kan du angi den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.CustomLocation%2A>egenskapen til denne plasseringen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.CustomLocation%2A>

trans-unit.source: **Log-File Name** - The base name for the log file is specified by the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.BaseFileName%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: **Loggen filnavn** -basis navnet for loggfilen er angitt i den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.BaseFileName%2A>egenskapen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.BaseFileName%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The current log file name can be read from the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: -Gjeldende loggfilnavn kan lese fra den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A>egenskapen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A>

trans-unit.source: It is derived from several other properties and the current state of the logs in the file system.
trans-unit.target: Den er utledet fra flere egenskaper og den gjeldende tilstanden til loggene i filsystemet.

trans-unit.source: **Log Maintenance** - The minimum frequency for creating new log files is determined by the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: **Logge Vedlikehold** -minste frekvensen for å opprette nye loggfiler fastsettes av den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A>egenskapen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the value is <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption> or <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption>, a new log file is created at least once every day or week, and a date stamp is incorporated into the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A> name.
trans-unit.target: Når verdien er <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption>eller <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption>, opprettes en ny loggfil minst én gang hver dag eller uke, og et datostempel er inkludert i den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A>navn.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.LogFileCreationScheduleOption>

trans-unit.source: - The maximum size (in bytes) of the log file is determined by the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.MaxFileSize%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: -Maksimale størrelse (i byte) av loggfilen fastsettes av den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.MaxFileSize%2A>egenskapen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.MaxFileSize%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the log file size exceeds this size, additional messages written to the log are discarded and, depending on the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.DiskSpaceExhaustedBehavior%2A> property, an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis loggfilstørrelsen overstiger denne grensen, flere meldinger som er skrevet til loggen er forkastet og, avhengig av <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.DiskSpaceExhaustedBehavior%2A>egenskapen et unntak.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.DiskSpaceExhaustedBehavior%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.ReserveDiskSpace%2A> property determines how much free space (in bytes) must be available.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.ReserveDiskSpace%2A>Egenskapen bestemmer hvor mye ledig plass (i byte) må være tilgjengelig.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.ReserveDiskSpace%2A>

trans-unit.source: This helps ensure that the FileLogTraceListener class will not consume all available disk space.
trans-unit.target: Dette sikrer at klassen FileLogTraceListener ikke vil bruke all tilgjengelig diskplass.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.DiskSpaceExhaustedBehavior%2A> property to specify the behavior of log writes when there are less than <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.ReserveDiskSpace%2A> bytes free.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.DiskSpaceExhaustedBehavior%2A>til å angi virkemåten for loggen skriver når det er mindre enn <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.ReserveDiskSpace%2A>byte ledig plass.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.ReserveDiskSpace%2A> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.DiskSpaceExhaustedBehavior%2A>

trans-unit.source: **Log-File Output Settings** - The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.AutoFlush%2A> property specifies whether the underlying stream should be flushed automatically after each write to the log file.
trans-unit.target: **Loggfilen utdatainnstillinger** - <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.AutoFlush%2A>egenskapen angir om den underliggende dataflyten skal tømmes automatisk etter hver skrive til loggfilen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.AutoFlush%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Append%2A> property specifies whether to append messages to the current log file, if allowed, or write them to a new log file.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Append%2A>Egenskapen angir om du vil tilføye meldinger i den gjeldende loggfilen hvis eller skrive dem til en ny loggfil.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Append%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Delimiter%2A> property specifies the string to use for delimiting the fields within a log message.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Delimiter%2A>Egenskapen angir strengen som skal brukes for som avgrenser felt i en loggmelding.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Delimiter%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Encoding%2A> property specifies the encoding to use when creating a new log file.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Encoding%2A>Egenskapen angir kodingen som skal brukes når du oppretter en ny loggfil.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Encoding%2A>

trans-unit.source: **Log-File Output** - The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.TraceData%2A> and <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.TraceEvent%2A> methods write messages to the log file.
trans-unit.target: **Loggfilen utdata** - <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.TraceData%2A>og <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.TraceEvent%2A>metoder skrive meldinger til loggfilen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.TraceEvent%2A> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.TraceData%2A>

trans-unit.source: These methods check the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A> property, along with any existing logs with the same base name to determine if a new log should be created.
trans-unit.target: Disse metodene se den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A>egenskapen sammen med alle eksisterende logger med grunntallet navnet å finne ut om det skal opprettes en ny logg.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Flush%2A> method flushes any messages currently in the output buffer to the log file.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Flush%2A>Metoden tømmer alle meldinger i utdatabufferen til loggfilen for øyeblikket.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Flush%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Close%2A> method closes the log file so that it can be used by other processes.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Close%2A>Metoden lukker loggfilen slik at den kan brukes av andre prosesser.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Close%2A>

trans-unit.source: **Enabling Output** You must enable tracing or debugging to use a trace listener.
trans-unit.target: **Aktivering av utdata** må du aktivere sporing eller feilsøking for å bruke en lytter for sporingen.

trans-unit.source: The following syntax is compiler specific.
trans-unit.target: Følgende syntaksen er kompilatoren bestemte.

trans-unit.source: If you use compilers other than C# or [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], refer to the documentation for your compiler.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du bruker kompilatorer enn C# eller [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], se dokumentasjonen for din kompilator.

trans-unit.source: - To enable debugging in C#, add the `/d:DEBUG` flag to the compiler command line when you compile your code, or you can add `#define DEBUG` to the top of your file.
trans-unit.target: -Feilsøking i C# du legge til den `/d:DEBUG` flagget kompilatoren kommandolinjen når du kompilerer koden, eller du kan legge til `#define DEBUG` til toppen av filen.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], add the `/d:DEBUG=True` flag to the compiler command line.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], legge til den `/d:DEBUG=True` flagget kompilatoren kommandolinjen.

trans-unit.source: - To enable tracing in C#, add the `/d:TRACE` flag to the compiler command line when you compile your code, or add `#define TRACE` to the top of your file.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis du vil aktivere sporing i C#, kan du legge til den `/d:TRACE` flagget kompilatoren kommandolinjen når du kompilere koden, eller Legg til `#define TRACE` til toppen av filen.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], add the `/d:TRACE=True` flag to the compiler command line.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], legge til den `/d:TRACE=True` flagget kompilatoren kommandolinjen.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether to append the output to the current file or write it to a new file.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om du vil tilføye utdataene den gjeldende filen eller skrive til en ny fil.

trans-unit.source: When the Append property is `False`, the output is written to a new file.
trans-unit.target: Når egenskapen Append er `False`, utdataene skrives til en ny fil.

trans-unit.source: When the property is `True`, the output is appended to the current file, unless: - The output file is locked by another process.
trans-unit.target: Når egenskapen er `True`, utdataene føyes til den gjeldende filen med mindre:-utdatafilen er låst av en annen prosess.

trans-unit.source: In this situation, a new log file is created with a version number that is incorporated into the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A> name.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet opprettes en ny loggfil med et versjonsnummer som er inkludert i den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A>navn.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The current file size is greater than what the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.MaxFileSize%2A> property allows.

trans-unit.source: In this situation, additional messages are discarded and, depending on the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.DiskSpaceExhaustedBehavior%2A> property, an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet flere meldinger er forkastet og, avhengig av <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.DiskSpaceExhaustedBehavior%2A>egenskapen et unntak.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.DiskSpaceExhaustedBehavior%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The existing file name is out of date according to the log-creation schedule specified by the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: -Det eksisterende filnavnet er for gammel i henhold til oppretting av loggen plan som er angitt av den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A>egenskapen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A>

trans-unit.source: In this situation, a new log file is created and the date stamp is incorporated into the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A> name.
trans-unit.target: I så fall opprettes en ny loggfil og Datostempelet er inkludert i den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A>navn.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.FullLogFileName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether or not the writing to the log file stream flushes the buffer.
trans-unit.target: Angir om skriving til loggen filstrøm Tømmer bufferen.

trans-unit.source: The `False` setting for the AutoFlush property provides the best performance for most applications, because it is more efficient to write multiple messages to the log file at one time.
trans-unit.target: Den `False` innstillingen for egenskapen AutoFlush gir best ytelse for de fleste programmer, fordi den er mer effektivt å skrive flere meldinger til loggfilen om gangen.

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Flush%2A> method to flush any messages currently in the log file's output buffer.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Flush%2A>metode for å tømme alle meldinger som loggfilen malens utdatanavn bufferen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Flush%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also use the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Close%2A> method, which implicitly flushes the stream before closing the log file.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også bruke den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Close%2A>metoden som implisitt Hurtigbuffertømminger dataflyten før du lukker loggfilen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Close%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_Boolean" name="Boolean" href=""></xref>, with <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> indicating that the stream is flushed after every write; otherwise the log entries are buffered and written more efficiently.
